{"members":[{"header_text":" اَلصَّدُوقُ فِي  اَلْمُقْنِعِ ، \"","body_text":"وَ لاَ تُجَامِعِ اِمْرَاَةً حَائِضاً فَاِنَّ اللَّهَ تَبَارَكَ وَ تَعَالَي نَهَي عَنْ ذَلِكَ فَقَالَ <quranic_text>«وَ لاٰ تَقْرَبُوهُنَّ حَتّٰي يَطْهُرْنَ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[البقرة۲۲۲]</footnote> .","translation":"","aligned_body":"وَ لاَ تُجَامِعِ اِمْرَاَةً حَائِضاً فَاِنَّ اللَّهَ تَبَارَكَ وَ تَعَالَي نَهَي عَنْ ذَلِكَ فَقَالَ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text وَ لاٰ تَقْرَبُوهُنَّ حَتّٰي يَطْهُرْنَ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote البقرة ۲۲۲ TAG_CLOSE:footnote"}],"body_consensus_columns":[{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"لا","display":"لاَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"تجامع","display":"تُجَامِعِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"امراه","display":"اِمْرَاَةً"},{"kind":"word","token":"حائضا","display":"حَائِضاً"},{"kind":"word","token":"فان","display":"فَاِنَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الله","display":"اللَّهَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"تبارك","display":"تَبَارَكَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"تعالي","display":"تَعَالَي"},{"kind":"word","token":"نهي","display":"نَهَي"},{"kind":"word","token":"عن","display":"عَنْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ذلك","display":"ذَلِكَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"فقال","display":"فَقَالَ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"لا","display":"لاٰ"},{"kind":"word","token":"تقربوهن","display":"تَقْرَبُوهُنَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"حتي","display":"حَتّٰي"},{"kind":"word","token":"يطهرن","display":"يَطْهُرْنَ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"البقره","display":"البقرة"},{"kind":"word","token":"۲۲۲","display":"۲۲۲"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"}]}